rows.label: xs33910100_MSG0010
rows.name: Oh no! Now cannot make entry![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33910100_MSG0020
rows.name: Lin, can you get us through?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33910100_MSG0050
rows.name:
It's got multiple layers of protection.
I could probably brute-force it, but it'd take a while.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33910100_MSG0060
rows.name:
Something tells me it might be quicker to just
track down the original release keys.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33910100_MSG0070
rows.name: Hm. In light of the situation...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33910100_MSG0080
rows.name:
I'd expect the Galdr who were here earlier
to be carrying those.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33910100_MSG0090
rows.name:
You think that's why they vamoosed?
To keep us from getting a hold of the keys?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33910100_MSG0100
rows.name: I'd say it's more than likely.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33910100_MSG0110
rows.name:
Tatsu cannot abide such cowardice!
We catch at once![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33910100_MSG0120
rows.name:
Let's run 'em down, wipe 'em out,
and get back those keys![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33910100_MSG0130
rows.name: Linly so ferocious! Like actual tyrant![ST:wait ]
